ready to proceed?

28:37.248 --> 28:38.981
Yes, your honor.

28:38.983 --> 28:41.451
Gentlemen, looks like we have a
plead ring that's been reached.

28:41.453 --> 28:44.454
Yes, subject to your approval...

28:44.456 --> 28:47.990
Uh, the defendant will plead no
contest to the lesser charges

28:47.992 --> 28:49.992
