28:49.994 --> 28:52.495
With the recommended
sentence of one year probation.

28:55.299 --> 28:56.499
Well...

28:58.001 --> 29:00.803
I've, uh, reviewed the record.

29:02.206 --> 29:05.374
Stipulation indicates that,

29:05.376 --> 29:08.411
the defendant's girlfriend suffered
a concussion and broken arm.

29:08.413 --> 29:11.447
