29:59.296 --> 30:00.797
Thank you very much.

30:03.133 --> 30:05.067
Hey, what are you
doing here, handsome?

30:05.569 --> 30:06.836
Had a hearing,

30:06.838 --> 30:08.304
I am too.
Just finishing up.

30:08.939 --> 30:10.239
That was John Altman.

30:10.241 --> 30:10.239
Senator?

30:10.241 --> 30:13.509
Son had too much to drink, got
a little rough with the date.

30:13.511 --> 30:14.877
What was the charge?

30:14.879 --> 30:17.246
Aggravated malicious wounding.

30:17.248 --> 30:19.148
How did she get
a domestic abuse felony

30:19.150 --> 30:21.217
reduced to a simple misdemeanor?

30:21.219 --> 30:22.885
The kind of money
the Altman's have,

30:22.887 --> 30:24.821
my entire staff's been working
on this case for two months.

30:24.823 --> 30:26.455
All they had to do was dig
up enough dirt on the girl,

30:26.457 --> 30:28.191
to blow holes
in her credibility.

30:28.193 --> 30:30.226
And you're not above
a cheap trick?

30:30.228 --> 30:33.262
Telling the judge that Wayne said he
didn't know how to try a criminal case?

30:33.264 --> 30:34.964
Hey, I didn't make it up.

30:35.299 --> 30:36.866
Besides,

30:36.868 --> 30:39.101
it's my job
to represent my client,

30:39.103 --> 30:41.504
