to celebrate alone.

31:04.962 --> 31:06.028
Just a drink.

31:17.307 --> 31:18.574
How'd it go?

31:23.447 --> 31:25.514
Good.
Fantastic.

31:25.516 --> 31:27.583
You have anymore
