31:29.420 --> 31:31.420
Great, let's celebrate,
let's get that drink.

31:32.089 --> 31:33.489
Yeah.

31:33.491 --> 31:36.125
I... can't.

31:36.127 --> 31:39.962
I'm sorry if I've misread
the situation, all right?

31:39.964 --> 31:41.497
I don't wanna
make you uncomfortable.

31:43.033 --> 31:44.567
