31:51.208 --> 31:52.675
A drink sounds good.

31:53.477 --> 31:55.278
Great, come on.

32:04.154 --> 32:06.522
She hasn't done anything to make you
think there's a problem, has she?

32:06.524 --> 32:09.724
She's probably not going to be too excited
about me living up here in the sticks.

32:11.628 --> 32:12.929
What about you?

32:13.530 --> 32:15.131
Is it hard not to drink?

32:15.966 --> 32:17.133
Sometimes.

32:19.236 --> 32:20.403
What makes it worse?

32:22.339 --> 32:23.572
I think too much.

32:24.274 --> 32:25.408
Thinking about what?

32:29.346 --> 32:30.980
It's kind of hard to explain.

32:34.251 --> 32:35.651
You don't know what
I'm really like.

32:38.221 --> 32:40.122
So...

32:40.124 --> 32:41.324
What are you really like?

32:43.026 --> 32:44.226
I'm, uh...

32:51.301 --> 32:52.468
Screwed up.

32:55.539 --> 32:57.039
That's not what
you were gonna say.

33:07.751 --> 33:09.685
You know...

33:09.687 --> 33:11.220
Why don't you stay over tonight?

33:12.189 --> 33:13.489
Go hiking in the morning?

33:13.491 --> 33:15.291
Oh, I wish I could.

33:15.293 --> 33:17.626
I have to get up early and
hit the office, I got a...

33:17.628 --> 33:19.228
Big hearing on Monday.

33:20.297 --> 33:21.764
Yeah, I should
probably work, too.

33:24.468 --> 33:26.335
But, we'll do this.

33:26.337 --> 33:28.170
No hiking.

33:28.172 --> 33:31.007
Just stay over tonight, we'll
leave first thing in the morning.

33:31.009 --> 33:33.309
I never really can sleep
well except in my own bed.

33:39.182 --> 33:40.449
Do you remember, Lee Darcy?

33:40.451 --> 33:42.651
You were representing
him when I met you.

33:42.653 --> 33:43.786
Yeah, I guess so.

33:45.589 --> 33:47.223
He was there, uh...

33:47.225 --> 33:49.558
