with a friend of mine.

33:49.560 --> 33:51.560
Why would a friend of yours
know someone like that?

33:53.096 --> 33:55.197
Funny, you should mention them.

33:55.199 --> 33:57.566
The neighbor came into
my office a while back,

33:57.568 --> 33:59.568
