33:59.570 --> 34:02.238
Apparently he didn't say he was
going to kill his girlfriend,

34:02.240 --> 34:04.106
but he split her head open.

34:04.108 --> 34:05.808
Probably banging
the neighbor now.

34:08.178 --> 34:10.146
No, he's still with
the girlfriend.

34:10.148 --> 34:12.415
She was on our hike, too.
Her name is Cathy.

34:12.417 --> 34:14.083
Cathy, yeah, yeah,
I remember her.

34:15.351 --> 34:16.719
Huh, doesn't surprise me,

34:16.721 --> 34:19.388
