35:45.876 --> 35:47.309
Sure is a pretty day.

35:48.178 --> 35:49.278
Yeah.

35:49.746 --> 35:51.514
It is.

35:51.516 --> 35:52.681
It's a great day for a hike.

35:53.183 --> 35:54.250
Yeah.

35:57.420 --> 35:58.888
This is a great spot.

36:01.191 --> 36:02.758
This is one of my favorites.

36:06.396 --> 36:07.630
You going any further?

36:09.699 --> 36:11.500
Thought I might head
up to Whitetop.

36:11.801 --> 36:12.868
Me, too.

36:13.837 --> 36:16.605
You hiking alone?
Yeah.

36:16.607 --> 36:18.841
Me, too all my
friends are tied up.

36:21.711 --> 36:24.313
I got the impression
they weren't that into hiking.

36:24.315 --> 36:25.848
They were...

36:25.850 --> 36:27.349
They were kind of colorful.

36:29.553 --> 36:31.520
I enjoyed meeting your
girlfriend, she was, uh...

36:32.189 --> 36:33.389
Pretty colorful.

36:34.891 --> 36:36.592
So you're arrogant
and you're gay?

36:38.929 --> 36:40.829
Yeah, I'm gay.

36:44.668 --> 36:46.569
Actually, I'm dating
George Wickham.

36:48.338 --> 36:51.640
Didn't he, uh,
defend you after you,

36:51.642 --> 36:53.375
