your girlfriend?

36:58.415 --> 36:59.481
Yeah.

37:02.753 --> 37:03.919
He did.

37:11.561 --> 37:14.230
Well, I'm gonna get going.

37:14.232 --> 37:15.297
I'll see you around.

37:35.819 --> 37:38.454
Okay, I give up.

37:39.856 --> 37:41.423
I actually have to take a break.

37:44.027 --> 37:45.294
Are we almost there?

37:45.662 --> 37:46.929
Yeah.

37:46.931 --> 37:48.364
We're really close.

37:49.432 --> 37:50.933
What's the surprise, anyway?

37:51.701 --> 37:52.901
You'll see.

37:52.903 --> 37:54.737
Come on, give me a hint.

37:57.007 --> 37:58.507
We were hiking all day.

38:00.877 --> 38:01.944
We're almost there.

38:02.879 --> 38:04.280
I promise.

38:05.649 --> 38:06.749
Come on.

40:04.901 --> 40:06.034
Hello?

40:06.636 --> 40:07.936
