everything to be so...

40:23.554 --> 40:24.753
Matchy-matchy.

40:24.755 --> 40:26.755
We need something
that pops and says,

40:26.757 --> 40:28.891
"wow, I'm here."

40:42.639 --> 40:43.939
What's wrong with you?

40:43.941 --> 40:45.574
You dirty little whore.

40:47.011 --> 40:49.088
You know, you two are so negative.
You're just... jealous.

40:49.112 --> 40:50.546
Jealous?

40:50.548 --> 40:52.714
We haven't even met
Mr. perfect yet.

40:52.716 --> 40:52.714
You'll get a chance to meet him.

40:52.716 --> 40:56.485
When Chuck has his little
party next weekend.

40:56.820 --> 40:58.821
At his cabin.

40:58.823 --> 41:00.856
You two are invited
for some bizarre reason.

41:00.858 --> 41:01.924
Really?

41:02.993 --> 41:04.059
It's George.

41:04.527 --> 41:05.794
Hey.

41:05.796 --> 41:07.062
Almost finished packing.

41:09.165 --> 41:10.232
Oh.

41:10.733 --> 41:11.834
Well...

41:12.769 --> 41:14.236
No, no, it's okay.

41:14.238 --> 41:16.572
I'll just cancel the hotel
and come over to your place.

41:17.540 --> 41:18.607
You sure?

41:20.477 --> 41:21.977
Okay.

41:21.979 --> 41:23.479
Try to get some sleep.

41:24.113 --> 41:25.481
Okay.

41:31.721 --> 41:33.755
George is ill.
Trip's off.

41:33.757 --> 41:35.190
What's wrong?

41:35.192 --> 41:36.959
He's been sick all morning.

41:36.961 --> 41:38.026
Hmmm.

41:38.261 --> 41:39.528
What?

41:44.534 --> 41:46.034
I should check on him.

41:47.971 --> 41:49.838
I don't know where he lives.

41:49.840 --> 41:51.106
You don't even know
where he lives?

41:51.108 --> 41:54.076
Yes, I know where
he lives, but I just...

41:54.078 --> 41:56.945
Haven't been to his place,
I don't know his address.

41:56.947 --> 41:58.547
I don't think
you should do that.

41:59.582 --> 42:01.783
He obviously told you
not to come over.

42:01.785 --> 42:03.519
Open your eyes, Shelby.

42:04.588 --> 42:06.688
Shelby, open your eyes.

42:07.790 --> 42:08.857
It's not funny.

42:09.526 --> 42:10.692
Not funny.

43:04.247 --> 43:05.647
What are you doing here?

43:06.583 --> 43:07.950
I just came to see how...

43:10.086 --> 43:11.620
Come on, daddy.

43:16.326 --> 43:17.693
Hello.

43:18.861 --> 43:21.263
Karen, this is Ben Bennett.

43:21.265 --> 43:22.864
Ben's an attorney at Abingdon.

43:23.900 --> 43:26.868
Ben, this is my wife, Karen.

43:30.073 --> 43:31.340
It's nice to meet you.

43:39.649 --> 43:42.017
I'm afraid you caught us
heading out for the weekend.

43:44.854 --> 43:46.355
I was just...

43:47.223 --> 43:48.624
Walking.

43:52.862 --> 43:54.062
I don't wanna keep you.

43:54.964 --> 43:57.366
Well, uh, good to see you again.

43:59.235 --> 44:00.302
Thanks.

45:39.335 --> 45:41.303
There really is a cabin.

45:43.073 --> 45:44.339
Great, look who it is.

45:49.078 --> 45:50.178
Hey.

45:50.947 --> 45:52.481
Hey, you made it.

45:52.483 --> 45:53.949
You had trouble
with the directions?

45:53.951 --> 45:55.417
No, they were great.

45:56.953 --> 45:59.354
Hey, thank you for having us.

45:59.356 --> 46:00.956
I'm glad you came.

46:00.958 --> 46:02.424
You guys know Lee and Cathy?

46:02.426 --> 46:03.859
Hey.
Hi.

46:05.294 --> 46:07.996
Where's George? Look
forward to meeting him.

46:07.998 --> 46:09.064
Um...

46:10.133 --> 46:11.533
Uh, it didn't work out.

46:12.769 --> 46:14.102
Oh, uh...

46:15.371 --> 46:17.305
Why don't we go inside and
I'll show you around.

46:18.841 --> 46:20.041
We'll be on the deck.

46:23.913 --> 46:25.413
This is my bedroom.

46:26.949 --> 46:28.884
Then through here
is the rest of the place.

46:45.334 --> 46:47.969
Oh, uh, may I use your bathroom?

46:47.971 --> 46:50.071
There's a slight problem.

46:50.073 --> 46:52.941
The Springs sometimes runs
dry this time of year.

46:52.943 --> 46:56.978
Well, uh, we won't have
water again until it rains.

46:56.980 --> 46:58.413
You'll have to use the outhouse.

47:00.449 --> 47:02.150
That's it, over there.

47:08.558 --> 47:10.058
Oh, uh...

47:10.593 --> 47:12.861
No problem, thanks.

47:14.463 --> 47:16.865
Hold up, back up,
I gotta see this, sorry.

47:18.568 --> 47:21.570
Sorry, we had water
until this morning.

47:22.205 --> 47:23.438
It's all right.

47:25.474 --> 47:26.875
Ah, do you wanna see the deck?

48:08.918 --> 48:10.051
Hey.

48:19.996 --> 48:22.716
You don't have to go. You don't have
to leave just 'cause I got here.

48:26.369 --> 48:29.304
I know it's not
any of my business, but...

48:29.306 --> 48:31.273
Why'd you plead guilty
to a felony?

48:33.976 --> 48:35.343
I don't want to talk about it.

48:36.445 --> 48:37.946
I'm an alcoholic.

48:40.082 --> 48:43.318
