the actual words.

49:04.440 --> 49:06.641
I was very drunk.

49:06.643 --> 49:08.510
Not that I'm using
this as an excuse.

49:09.712 --> 49:11.947
I take full responsibility
for what I did.

49:14.483 --> 49:16.351
I just don't remember
the details.

49:18.220 --> 49:20.288
I understand I said,

49:20.290 --> 49:22.557
"I'll kill you",
when I pushed her.

49:22.559 --> 49:24.259
Where was the evidence
that you said that?

49:26.095 --> 49:27.963
Well, my neighbor
heard me say it.

49:28.998 --> 49:31.733
And my attorney, George.

49:33.202 --> 49:36.271
He said, I didn't have
a defense because...

49:36.273 --> 49:37.633
There was
an independent witness...

49:38.307 --> 49:40.241
Testifying against me.

49:40.243 --> 49:41.723
And I have no memory
of what happened.

49:44.613 --> 49:46.348
Did George interview
the neighbor?

49:48.286 --> 49:49.185
No.

49:49.186 --> 49:54.089
But, uh, the policeman
took her statement.

49:54.091 --> 49:55.423
Did Cathy say
you threatened her?

49:55.425 --> 49:57.158
She doesn't really
remember what happened.

49:57.160 --> 49:58.393
Look...

49:58.395 --> 50:00.095
I didn't intend
to get into all this.

50:01.163 --> 50:02.731
I messed up.

50:02.733 --> 50:04.599
I had a job lined up in Atlanta.

50:04.601 --> 50:06.501
Cathy and I were going
to move down there.

50:06.503 --> 50:09.504
But in a strange way,
it's better.

50:09.506 --> 50:11.506
I'm finally taking
responsibility for my actions.

50:13.175 --> 50:15.110
Making excuses
doesn't change anything.

50:20.116 --> 50:23.518
I'm really sorry about what I
said, the day of your hearing.

50:23.520 --> 50:25.387
I didn't know you were there.

50:25.389 --> 50:26.788
I wasn't thinking about
what I was saying,

50:26.790 --> 50:28.790
I didn't have any idea
of what I was saying.

50:30.526 --> 50:31.760
I'm really sorry.

50:32.595 --> 50:33.762
Lee.

50:38.401 --> 50:39.768
I better go.

51:08.197 --> 51:09.330
Almost ready.

51:09.332 --> 51:10.398
Oh, great.

51:14.837 --> 51:16.371
Looks like we're just in time.

51:16.373 --> 51:17.505
Yeah.

51:17.507 --> 51:18.840
Need help with anything?

51:18.842 --> 51:21.543
Um, so yeah, I need
to run inside.

51:21.545 --> 51:23.111
You better let me handle this.

51:25.114 --> 51:26.381
Has anyone seen Ben?

51:53.642 --> 51:55.410
Lee, would you mind
saying the blessing?

51:57.613 --> 52:00.482
Okay, um...

52:01.817 --> 52:04.419
Dear god, thank you

52:04.787 --> 52:06.121
for...

52:06.489 --> 52:07.689
Um...

52:09.592 --> 52:12.660
