52:12.662 --> 52:14.696
to accept the things
we cannot change,

52:14.698 --> 52:17.332
the courage to change
the things we can

52:17.334 --> 52:19.200
and the wisdom
to know the difference.

52:19.802 --> 52:20.869
Amen.

52:20.871 --> 52:22.670
Amen.

52:24.807 --> 52:28.309
So, Ben, what happened
with you and your boyfriend?

52:30.412 --> 52:31.613
