faster than a wife and kids.

52:51.267 --> 52:54.569
No, but, you know,
what I mean, I mean...

52:54.571 --> 52:57.872
You guys are always running
around having sex with each other

52:57.874 --> 53:00.308
in public bathrooms,
truck stops.

53:02.444 --> 53:06.614
